# Testing New Class and ID Syntax

## Basic Examples
__.my-button Primary Button|Click Me__
__.success-label#important Label|Important__
__.custom-segment#info Segment|Information content__

## Multiple Classes
__.btn.btn-primary.btn-large#submit-btn Primary Button|Submit__
__.label-info.label-large#status-badge Label|Status__

## Complex Examples
__.navigation-menu#main-nav Menu|[Home](#) [About](#) [Contact](#)__
__.data-table#users-table Table|Name,Email,Role|John,john@example.com,Admin|Jane,jane@example.com,User__

## Form with Classes and IDs
__.contact-form#registration-form Form:
> __Field|First Name__
> __.form-input#name-field Input|Enter your name__
> __.submit-btn#submit-btn Primary Button|Submit__
